DropDowns
DropDowns i a menu which gives us an opportunity to select one or more options

type of DropDowns;
1.Single Select
2.Multiple Select;

Handling DropDown;
1.click on dropdowns and click on option
2.using Select Class
                  in order to use Select class
                  we need to make sure our dropdown has
                  a Select tag

 Selection an option from a dropdown can be done in 3 ways:
 1.bu index
 2.by visible
 3.by value

Whenever you interact with multiple elements you store them inside the container
such as List,set et

In order to deselect the option from dropdown
--Make sure your DD is multiply select
deselectByValuy;
deselectByIndex;
deselectByVisibleText;
deselectAll;















